The '''Mandalorian Armed Forces''' were the forces that [[Governor/Legends|Governor]] [[Vrox]] sent to raid [[Star system/Legends|star systems]] neighboring the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Mandalore/Legends|Mandalore]]. It was because of this that the [[Republican Army]] was sent to Mandalore with a group of [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] to capture him.<ref name="BFM">{{ChallengeCite|58|Battle for Mandalore}}</ref>

